    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hack</strong>, <strong>Slash </strong>and <strong>Carve up </strong>waves as you journey across the Surf Realms. On your quest to unite or conquer the <strong>Coast </strong>you’ll need to evolve from humble kook to certified <strong>Lord of the Waves.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Win contests</strong>, go <strong>head to head</strong> with other surfers, <strong>earn prizes, </strong>or <strong>Free Surf</strong>. Whether you consider yourself a Star or a Soul Surfer, craft your own style on the ocean.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Coast is in Disharmony.</strong> The once sacred art of Surfriding is being sucked dry by the corporate overlords who treasure coins over stoke. As beaches are swarmed with kooks, Surf lords emerge to protect their Realms. Everywhere, things are totally un-chill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can Surfing be saved? Can balance be restored to the realm? It will take someone totally radical, but also super chill...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Be one with the wave</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use speed, style and timing to execute big tricks and combinations. Each wave is a canvas for you to carve out points. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/748776b654291e1ad903aec78c8de174.poster.avif?t=1728132367\" width=680 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/748776b654291e1ad903aec78c8de174.webm?t=1728132367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/748776b654291e1ad903aec78c8de174.mp4?t=1728132367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Soak in the Vibes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cruise through psychedelic Surf Realms with their own style and soundscape. Experience different types of waves, crowds and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/31e7683c329fe9e5382ab6b5e6b559df.poster.avif?t=1728132367\" width=680 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/31e7683c329fe9e5382ab6b5e6b559df.webm?t=1728132367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/31e7683c329fe9e5382ab6b5e6b559df.mp4?t=1728132367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Journey</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete against other Surfers, earn sponsorships, enter knockout tournaments or roam at your own pleasure. The ocean is yours…   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/84640b119c9be2e77f8df0e3ba47e46d.poster.avif?t=1728132367\" width=680 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/84640b119c9be2e77f8df0e3ba47e46d.webm?t=1728132367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/84640b119c9be2e77f8df0e3ba47e46d.mp4?t=1728132367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Express Yourself</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your Surfboards, learn new tricks and craft your own trippy style. Become the ultimate Surf Lord… <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/a10e81d3ca464b67a934a162703f4e6b.poster.avif?t=1728132367\" width=680 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/a10e81d3ca464b67a934a162703f4e6b.webm?t=1728132367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/a10e81d3ca464b67a934a162703f4e6b.mp4?t=1728132367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new abilities, buy new gear and create your own style to stand out on the waves.</p>",
